
HERPASURFING is an open source Cyber Security Solution

For Information or questions: sherpasurfing@gmail.com


SHERPA is based on the CLOUDERA stack and will provide the following:

Enrichment Sources - The Enrichment Branch is provided for all of the Cyber Security enrichment sources and services provided by the contributors of the project. 

Contrib - The Contributor Branch is provided for the submission by contributors of the SHERPASURFING Project

Doc - All Documentation for the project

Cookbook - The Cookbook will not be considered to be system documentation. This is provided for more of a howto guide based on successful analytic patterns.

Framework - The service framework for SHERPA

